Contents
Problem




DataManagerFwd.hpp
Forward declarations + DM_DataType enum
Lives inside DataManager; no way to link it independently


DataManagerTypes.hpp
DataTypeVariant typedef + IODataType bridge
Includes DataManagerFwd.hpp + IOTypes.hpp + &lt;variant&gt;



The fix is two independent INTERFACE libraries at different weight classes:


