With DataTypeEnum as a zero-dependency INTERFACE library, the IO system links it directly. IODataType has been eliminated.
What was removed: - IO/core/IOTypes.hpp (the IODataType enum) - toIODataType() / fromIODataType() conversion functions in DataManagerTypes.hpp - All static_assert sync checks between the two enums
