Located in Entity/Lineage/LineageTypes.hpp, defines 8 lineage strategies as a std::variant:








Type
Description
Use Case




Source
Root data with no parent
Raw loaded data


OneToOneByTime
1:1 mapping at each time point
MaskData → Area values


AllToOneByTime
N:1 aggregation at each time
Sum of all areas at time T


SubsetLineage
Filtered subset of source
Excluded/selected entities


MultiSourceLineage
Multiple sources combined
Merged datasets


ExplicitLineage
